{"tid":1658542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家專注好分工","createTime":"2019-10-16T13:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T14:03:02.000Z","uid":167145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"488c57e553e0234d359135068ed07162e8522050","tid":1658542,"uid":167145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:50:49.000Z","msg":"我講既分工 係指對事上分工<br />\n岑子杰遇襲 大家都嬲 星期日上街亦係唔會改變既事實<br />\n呢個PO純粹想大家諗多小小野 點解會係呢個時候遇襲 偏偏係人權案通過後? <br />\n如上面所講 大家一定會嬲 但我唔建議全部風向去晒一件事上<br />\n大家除左嬲之餘希望可以留意下今日有無特別奇怪既事發生 又或者係咪跟開既案有新進展政府怕人知道?<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">1. 陳彥霖案</span></strong><br />\n純粹根據好多巴打討論後個人既推測<br />\n佢可能真係一早死左 然後有人除晒佢衫扮佢回校 再到而家既CCTV事件 亦解釋到點解佢會全裸 (當然唔排除被強姦說法)<br />\n跟開呢單事既巴打 請都專注返<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">2. 疑似解放軍醫院處理手足事件</span></strong><br />\nSorry 呢個我無深入了解 但我都覺得呢個係政府唔想大家去查既事 跟開呢單事既巴打請都專注返 因為可能會突破條盲腸<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">3. 分化</span></strong><br />\n連登近排咩事大家都明 唔想講太多 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">4. 惡法</span></strong><br />\n送中條例撤回一說大家都知係大話 請記得送中議題已被delay<br />\n亦請多多留意政府文件 有無奇怪改動或惡法推出<br />\n跟開既手足麻煩晒<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">5. 觀塘割狗事件</span></strong><br />\n對於小事都放大既黑警 CCTV 政府竟然無告謀殺 大家其實都心照<br />\n但請繼續發大佢 唔好走漏任何踢爆公安武警解放軍混入警隊既消息<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">6. 印尼記者中彈事件</span></strong><br />\n呢件事我自己覺得係真。核彈 (當然好多手足受傷都係 但今次係國際記者)<br />\n核彈呢個Term用到悶 我真係唔建議巴打你地打打加核彈係Topic到 因為真係會confuse好多人<br />\n印尼中彈事件到今日警方亦未交出開槍警員 (明明UPS影到)<br />\n所以希望大家都比返D心機focus返係呢件事上 亦係我地打進國際線既好好籌碼"},{"pid":"e5e7db35b89126080e0b7801e87edf37bf70f946","tid":1658542,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:51:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23d4844117e8890744d12cd12b20479667c3c86b","tid":1658542,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:51:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8fce561136ad9812fe9cc3e6c947cf27286016b3","tid":1658542,"uid":167145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:55:38.000Z","msg":"請大家謹守崗位"},{"pid":"ce8106c94b6741dd1edcbb57241b0dc012387e5e","tid":1658542,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:56:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ebc1caf06040c079d0f6dfee58750a2a1941ede","tid":1658542,"uid":167145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:01:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c54120279a1e3a00477d8ccb570ab90c4fad11c","tid":1658542,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:03:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老母岑子杰單野我要響國際新聞見到！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658212</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n全世界同我落<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#PrayForJimmy</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得寫係ProBeijing Red Thugs 做！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁撚大件事同我講畀國際知呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\ntwitter組已經將所有link放左上bot<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">入 /task3 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9SryzC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D